title: Koisuru YouTuber
original_name: 恋するユーチューバー
sinopse:
Mina is a makeup YouTuber, and Yuugo is a gaming YouTuber. One day, Mina finds out that Yuugo is secretly handsome, and asks him to be in her YouTube videos. But eventually, she begins to have feelings for him!

(Source: Shogakukan, translated)

Included one-shot: Gachi Koi YouTuber
